column1: The independent resource on global security

column4: <li> The SIPRI Arms Transfers Database does not contain any information on deliveries or orders for the suppliers, recipients and time period specified.

column1: For more information on the coverage of the database, see http://www.sipri.org/databases/armstransfers/background/coverage.

SIPRI is an independent international institute dedicated to research into conflict, armaments, arms control and disarmament. Established in 1966, SIPRI provides data, analysis and recommendations, based on open sources.
